&lt;a href="https://pages.github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;GitHub pages&lt;/a&gt;, and you want the site to be indexed
by Google, it&amp;rsquo;s not so easy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m not sure entirely what the root cause is, but you have to manually add your
site in the 



&lt;a href="https://search.google.com/search-console" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Google Search Console&lt;/a&gt;
and then manually add each URL individually for indexing.





 
 
 
 
 
 

 
 
 
 
 

 
 
 
 
 

 
 

